sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant DesktopApp as Desktop Application
    participant System as System

    User->>DesktopApp: Launch Application
    DesktopApp->>System: Request Data
    System-->>DesktopApp: Send Data
    DesktopApp-->>User: Display Data
    User->>DesktopApp: Interact with Application
    DesktopApp->>System: Update Data
    System-->>DesktopApp: Confirm Update
    DesktopApp-->>User: Show Update Confirmation